1
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:18,110
[Longwan Village, Hanzhou City, 2005]

2
00:00:36,280 --> 00:00:36,940
Xiaoshuai?

3
00:00:41,430 --> 00:00:43,630
What are you doing here? Why not come in?

4
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:44,390
I...

5
00:00:45,600 --> 00:00:47,060
Wait. Why did you come out?

6
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:48,220
For some fresh air,

7
00:00:48,220 --> 00:00:49,750
since I had too many drinks.

8
00:00:50,210 --> 00:00:51,740
Check out what I bought you.

9
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:53,840
What is it?

10
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:56,110
"What is it?" A gift it is.

11
00:00:57,670 --> 00:00:58,470
Just this one?

12
00:00:58,990 --> 00:01:00,460
How many more do you want?

13
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:02,920
Alright.

14
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:04,150
Congratulations.

15
00:01:04,150 --> 00:01:06,550
I'd better call you Officer Wen
from now on.

16
00:01:07,350 --> 00:01:08,460
Cut it out.

17
00:01:09,350 --> 00:01:10,150
Listen,

18
00:01:10,590 --> 00:01:12,200
we'll be best buddies forever.

19
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:13,710
Even when we're old and gray,

20
00:01:13,710 --> 00:01:14,930
I'll still be Bo,

21
00:01:15,130 --> 00:01:16,590
and you'll still be Xiaoshuai.

22
00:01:16,590 --> 00:01:17,120
Got it?

23
00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:19,280
Can you stop with this mushy stuff?

24
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,210
I'm telling you,

25
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:22,840
I'm not sure
if I'll still be this handsome by then,

26
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,170
but you surely won't be.

27
00:01:25,470 --> 00:01:27,400
What, you think you won't age, huh?

28
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:29,039
If I lose my looks, you'll lose yours too.

29
00:01:29,039 --> 00:01:30,640
Stop it. It sounds terrible.

30
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:32,620
So you do know it sounds terrible.

31
00:02:42,410 --> 00:02:52,770
[The Punishment]

32
00:02:52,910 --> 00:02:53,150
[Punish those who commit crimes
and make mistakes]

33
00:02:53,150 --> 00:02:53,390
[so as to discipline them,]

34
00:02:53,390 --> 00:02:53,880
[and execute those
who violate the prohibitions]

35
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:54,850
[so as to terrify would-be violators.]

36
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:56,790
[Guanzi – On Laws and Standards]

37
00:02:57,450 --> 00:03:00,380
[Episode 26]

38
00:03:39,570 --> 00:03:40,200
Tianye.

39
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,280
The police have traced the money

40
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,540
we gave Mrs. Wen and Bo.

41
00:03:46,140 --> 00:03:46,980
It was He Biao.

42
00:03:47,850 --> 00:03:49,810
He Biao must've tipped them off.

43
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:52,740
As I told you before,

44
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:57,030
we should've informed Mrs. Wen and Bo
beforehand.

45
00:03:57,650 --> 00:03:58,800
Now, look what has happened.

46
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,430
They

47
00:03:59,430 --> 00:04:01,290
haven't got to spend a penny of it.

48
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:03,420
We've even got Bo in a heap of trouble.

49
00:04:04,550 --> 00:04:05,480
Now, think about

50
00:04:05,670 --> 00:04:07,800
how we're going to explain to Mrs. Wen.

51
00:04:08,530 --> 00:04:09,360
This is my fault.

52
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,920
My recklessness caused Bo trouble.

53
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:11,630
I'll be responsible,

54
00:04:11,630 --> 00:04:12,830
explain everything,

55
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:15,390
and state that the money has nothing to do
with Mrs. Wen and Bo.

56
00:04:15,390 --> 00:04:16,680
Who are you going to say that to?

57
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,540
Are you able to clear their names?

58
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,200
Then what do you suggest?

59
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:22,040
If Bo's really jeopardized by us
and lose his job

60
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,170
as a police officer,

61
00:04:24,190 --> 00:04:25,400
how can we face Jiangyong

62
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:26,310
and his wife?

63
00:04:26,430 --> 00:04:27,870
S-So what if he loses his job?

64
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:28,920
It's not that big of a deal.

65
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,080
Worst case, he can join us.

66
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:31,750
Liu Tianfei! Do you even hear yourself?

67
00:04:31,750 --> 00:04:33,350
What's all this yelling for?

68
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:35,720
Bo and Mrs. Wen

69
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,650
didn't know about the money at all.

70
00:04:42,830 --> 00:04:44,230
What's our priority now?

71
00:04:45,070 --> 00:04:46,830
It's to keep them from figuring out

72
00:04:46,830 --> 00:04:48,070
our real business.

73
00:04:53,190 --> 00:04:53,870
Tianye,

74
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,000
there are still some goods around.

75
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,540
We must quickly remove them
and clean the mess,

76
00:04:59,540 --> 00:05:01,800
especially the cash in the cold storage.

77
00:05:04,020 --> 00:05:05,220
How to transfer them?

78
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,560
Contact Uncle Limin.

79
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,620
There are empty warehouses

80
00:05:14,620 --> 00:05:15,880
at the port he manages.

81
00:05:16,890 --> 00:05:17,890
It's safer there.

82
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:31,450
Mrs. Wen's calling.

83
00:05:31,450 --> 00:05:35,190
[Incoming: Mrs. Wen]

84
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:44,920
Mrs. Wen.

85
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,900
The procuratorate called me.

86
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,880
I demand an explanation.

87
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,400
That money...

88
00:05:54,890 --> 00:05:56,420
was meant for you and Bo.

89
00:05:56,450 --> 00:05:57,850
But since you refused it,

90
00:05:58,250 --> 00:05:59,450
I saved it up for you.

91
00:05:59,750 --> 00:06:01,480
What gave you the right to do so?

92
00:06:02,190 --> 00:06:04,450
You've got Bo in hot water! You know that?

93
00:06:04,610 --> 00:06:06,000
Don't you know why I never used

94
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,480
that money?

95
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,680
Mrs. Wen,

96
00:06:10,390 --> 00:06:11,200
I'm sorry.

97
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,920
But rest assured.

98
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,160
We promise to keep Bo from harm.

99
00:06:15,950 --> 00:06:16,800
Jiangyong

100
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:18,310
had a share in that money too, so...

101
00:06:18,310 --> 00:06:20,840
You even have the nerve
to mention Jiangyong!

102
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:29,610
Mrs. Wen,

103
00:06:31,690 --> 00:06:32,420
actually...

104
00:06:32,530 --> 00:06:34,050
the money is not dirty.

105
00:06:34,590 --> 00:06:35,920
We just wanted you and Bo

106
00:06:36,090 --> 00:06:37,290
to have a better life.

107
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:39,720
We were doing fine without that money.

108
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:42,159
If you truly want the best for Bo,

109
00:06:42,470 --> 00:06:44,120
then keep a distance from him.

110
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,630
Get as far away as you can!

111
00:07:15,310 --> 00:07:16,160
Tianye.

112
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,610
Come in here with me.

113
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:39,380
[House of Benevolence]

114
00:07:39,380 --> 00:07:40,060
Kneel.

115
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:49,830
Kneel!

116
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:57,560
[House of Benevolence]

117
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,440
Tianye,

118
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:01,070
today, before our ancestors,

119
00:08:01,870 --> 00:08:03,600
answer my questions honestly.

120
00:08:04,050 --> 00:08:05,060
Now, tell me,

121
00:08:05,210 --> 00:08:07,470
where did the money you gave Bo come from?

122
00:08:08,310 --> 00:08:10,240
The profits of Longwan Logistics.

123
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:16,350
Tianye,

124
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:21,150
it's been less than 3 years
since you thought of

125
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:23,760
founding this company till this moment.

126
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:26,950
Now you're saying that you spared as much

127
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:29,010
as 5 million for Bo from your profits.

128
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:31,600
How are we supposed to believe that?

129
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,440
Over the past 3 years,

130
00:08:34,740 --> 00:08:36,940
we've truly caught the logistics boom.

131
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:39,169
Everyone has made good money.

132
00:08:39,669 --> 00:08:40,510
So I,

133
00:08:41,150 --> 00:08:42,890
Peng, Taoyi, and Tianfei

134
00:08:43,669 --> 00:08:45,600
contributed some of our earnings,

135
00:08:45,910 --> 00:08:47,800
plus dividends
from several other companies,

136
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:48,200
[House of Benevolence]

137
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,600
and pooled them together

138
00:08:50,050 --> 00:08:51,450
to make up this 5 million.

139
00:08:52,630 --> 00:08:53,550
Jiangyong...

140
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:56,620
was one of Longwan Logistics' founders.

141
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:58,160
He didn't get to live a good life.

142
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,030
[In Memory of the Liu Family's Ancestors]

143
00:08:59,030 --> 00:08:59,890
So we wanted to improve the lives

144
00:08:59,890 --> 00:09:01,450
[In Memory of the Wen Family's Ancestors]

145
00:09:01,470 --> 00:09:01,740
[In Memory of the Qin Family's Ancestors]

146
00:09:01,740 --> 00:09:02,830
of his wife and son.

147
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:04,600
That's all.

148
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,600
Is this money clean?

149
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,360
Yes.

150
00:09:08,970 --> 00:09:09,880
Are you sure?

151
00:09:09,910 --> 00:09:11,120
I am sure, Mom.

152
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:13,970
I just don't get it.

153
00:09:14,750 --> 00:09:15,570
In only 3 years,

154
00:09:15,570 --> 00:09:16,480
Longwan Logistics

155
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:18,810
has soared to such heights like a rocket.

156
00:09:19,390 --> 00:09:21,200
Have you really not done anything shady?

157
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,630
What don't you understand, Mom?

158
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:24,480
What makes you doubt me? As I told you,

159
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,510
these few years are golden times

160
00:09:25,510 --> 00:09:26,910
for logistics business.

161
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,350
Besides, I said a long time ago

162
00:09:28,350 --> 00:09:30,390
that Longwan could produce high profits.

163
00:09:30,390 --> 00:09:32,020
Why did everyone target this land?

164
00:09:32,020 --> 00:09:33,600
Because they saw the potential in it.

165
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:35,550
Am I wrong for using it
to make money myself?

166
00:09:35,550 --> 00:09:36,670
No, you're not wrong.

167
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:38,130
Making money isn't wrong.

168
00:09:38,830 --> 00:09:40,390
We the Longwan people have always

169
00:09:40,390 --> 00:09:42,590
been upright in character and conduct.

170
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:44,330
Listen,

171
00:09:44,550 --> 00:09:46,610
if you make money by dirty means—

172
00:09:46,670 --> 00:09:47,910
be it for the good of Longwan—

173
00:09:47,910 --> 00:09:49,910
you'll end up reaping bitter fruit!

174
00:09:50,550 --> 00:09:51,240
Son, you...

175
00:09:52,030 --> 00:09:54,070
You're destroying Longwan

176
00:09:54,090 --> 00:09:55,550
and leading it down a path of no return

177
00:09:55,550 --> 00:09:57,120
with what you're doing now!

178
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:01,300
Since when...

179
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:05,520
Since when have you become
completely different?

180
00:10:07,970 --> 00:10:13,200
[House of Benevolence]

181
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:26,630
Mom.

182
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:33,120
The time has come
to save Longwan Logistics.

183
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:33,910
Issue a notice

184
00:10:33,910 --> 00:10:36,150
that a shareholders' meeting
will be held in a few days.

185
00:10:36,150 --> 00:10:36,630
Mom...

186
00:10:37,180 --> 00:10:40,540
[Ancestral Hall
of the Liu, Wen, and Qin Families]

187
00:10:47,370 --> 00:10:51,550
[House of Benevolence]

188
00:10:53,270 --> 00:10:55,120
Your actions had better align

189
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:57,510
with your declaration

190
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:02,020
to compensate Jiangyong,
so he'd rest in peace.

191
00:11:06,520 --> 00:11:07,800
It doesn't matter

192
00:11:07,920 --> 00:11:09,180
if you're rich or poor.

193
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:11,490
Just don't take the wrong path.

194
00:11:19,420 --> 00:11:25,360
[House of Benevolence]

195
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:41,240
[Incoming: He Biao]

196
00:11:41,350 --> 00:11:47,220
[House of Benevolence]

197
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:48,630
Liu Tianye.

198
00:11:50,390 --> 00:11:53,190
Longwan Logistics has made the news.
Are you okay?

199
00:11:53,890 --> 00:11:55,120
You called me so soon.

200
00:11:55,740 --> 00:11:58,070
Why not worry about your brother instead?

201
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,960
Let's skip that crap.

202
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,040
Without my approval,

203
00:12:04,790 --> 00:12:07,050
you'll never make it to the inner circle.

204
00:12:07,630 --> 00:12:09,630
I don't care if I'll make it that far.

205
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:11,640
But if you dare target my family,

206
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:14,080
I'll definitely ruin everything for you.

207
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,030
Liu Tianye.

208
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,240
Thank you.

209
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:20,500
I've been acting as Muzhi for so long.

210
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:25,580
Today, I finally get to be Biao again.

211
00:12:51,390 --> 00:12:51,990
Tianye.

212
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:57,050
Madam Wen plans to hold
a shareholders' meeting.

213
00:12:57,690 --> 00:12:59,150
A shareholders' meeting?

214
00:13:01,270 --> 00:13:02,200
What is she up to?

215
00:13:03,630 --> 00:13:04,630
My mother intends

216
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:06,780
to kick us all out of the corporation.

217
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:09,320
Well...

218
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:11,720
What should we do?

219
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,750
She's canvassing shareholders.

220
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:14,750
We can do that too.

221
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,550
That's not the most urgent issue now.

222
00:13:17,550 --> 00:13:19,200
The allegations against Longwan Logistics

223
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,360
have gone viral.

224
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:23,480
Our cooperation with Xinrui
must be paused.

225
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:24,940
That's what He Biao wants.

226
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:25,910
If we hit the brakes,

227
00:13:25,910 --> 00:13:27,570
he'll get a chance to swoop in.

228
00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:29,200
What?

229
00:13:29,870 --> 00:13:32,030
Hasn't he admitted defeat
as he's already doomed?

230
00:13:32,030 --> 00:13:34,430
Is he still dreaming of
turning the tables?

231
00:13:37,510 --> 00:13:39,350
Tell our people to get prepared.

232
00:13:39,380 --> 00:13:41,120
Cut ties with those subsidiary companies.

233
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:42,670
The police will track them down soon.

234
00:13:42,670 --> 00:13:43,510
Got it.

235
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,580
Any news about He Gang?

236
00:13:45,630 --> 00:13:47,120
We've searched every hospital in the city.

237
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:48,320
No trail of him at all.

238
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,530
Could he have fled?

239
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:52,720
Anyway,
if he doesn't have his wounds treated,

240
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:54,070
he'll definitely die.

241
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:59,350
As I recall, He Biao knows Dr. Chen
from the City Second Hospital.

242
00:13:59,360 --> 00:13:59,910
Right.

243
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:00,650
Exactly.

244
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,200
They know each other.

245
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,760
Dr. Chen is a freeloader

246
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:04,670
and a gambler,

247
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:07,700
who has lost a lot of money
at He Biao's place.

248
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:09,750
Why not ask him,

249
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:12,140
now that we can't find He Gang?

250
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,520
I remember Dr. Chen has

251
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:16,190
a thing for...

252
00:14:16,910 --> 00:14:17,870
Zhou Sisi.

253
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:26,990
[Hanzhou Public Security]

254
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:31,120
Qin Feng...

255
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:34,000
I've supervised him for 2 years,

256
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:36,580
and Wen Bo for quite some time too.

257
00:14:36,910 --> 00:14:38,240
Whatever cases they handled,

258
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:41,240
they never complained,
even in the face of hardships.

259
00:14:41,510 --> 00:14:42,640
I have faith in them.

260
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:45,820
I don't believe
they'd yield to temptation.

261
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:49,140
Doubtlessly,

262
00:14:49,910 --> 00:14:51,390
they're good officers.

263
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:55,690
But good officers might also take bribes.

264
00:14:55,910 --> 00:14:58,040
It happened before within the system.

265
00:14:59,300 --> 00:15:00,430
So, I suggest

266
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:02,380
in a time like this,

267
00:15:03,110 --> 00:15:03,750
we must...

268
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:06,320
conduct a thorough investigation.

269
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:08,010
We have to uncover the truth

270
00:15:08,670 --> 00:15:10,400
and clear our comrades' names.

271
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:11,760
In addition,

272
00:15:12,910 --> 00:15:13,720
shall we...

273
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:16,150
temporarily reassign officers

274
00:15:17,510 --> 00:15:19,370
who are in sensitive situations?

275
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:21,500
Are you suggesting...

276
00:15:22,510 --> 00:15:24,360
Qin Feng should be reassigned?

277
00:15:24,790 --> 00:15:25,870
It's a suggestion

278
00:15:25,870 --> 00:15:27,070
open for discussion.

279
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:27,880
As it happens,

280
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:29,120
Ganghang Public Security Bureau

281
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:30,550
has always wanted to have him over.

282
00:15:30,550 --> 00:15:31,510
I think this is

283
00:15:31,510 --> 00:15:33,240
a perfect opportunity.

284
00:15:34,160 --> 00:15:34,980
For one thing,

285
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,940
Ganghang Bureau will be stronger

286
00:15:37,030 --> 00:15:38,120
with him onboard.

287
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:39,960
For another thing, to him,

288
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:42,270
it's a change of environment and mindset.

289
00:15:42,270 --> 00:15:43,240
The main purpose

290
00:15:44,550 --> 00:15:45,690
to calm

291
00:15:45,870 --> 00:15:47,440
public sentiment.

292
00:15:51,030 --> 00:15:52,630
Who else would like to speak?

293
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:55,600
Director Ye,

294
00:15:55,720 --> 00:15:56,850
may I have the floor?

295
00:15:57,470 --> 00:15:58,330
Sure. Go ahead.

296
00:16:00,970 --> 00:16:02,990
Qin Feng is just a precinct captain.

297
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:06,210
What's the point of transferring him?

298
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,240
I'm head
of the Criminal Investigation Unit.

299
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,100
It should be me,

300
00:16:10,550 --> 00:16:11,750
if anyone is to be transferred.

301
00:16:11,750 --> 00:16:12,960
We did attempt to transfer you there,

302
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:15,620
but you were extremely reluctant,
weren't you?

303
00:16:16,870 --> 00:16:17,930
From where I stand,

304
00:16:18,790 --> 00:16:20,320
Longwan Logistics' matter

305
00:16:20,550 --> 00:16:21,550
is not necessarily connected

306
00:16:21,550 --> 00:16:23,150
to Qin Feng and Wen Bo.

307
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:26,520
Such a thing is happening
as we're halfway through

308
00:16:26,580 --> 00:16:28,710
the investigation on the He brothers.

309
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:31,440
Someone is clearly trying to sabotage it.

310
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:34,120
What does this indicate?

311
00:16:34,510 --> 00:16:36,640
It indicates we're on the right track.

312
00:16:38,790 --> 00:16:40,520
Now, if Qin Feng is transferred

313
00:16:42,290 --> 00:16:43,750
just over some negative buzz,

314
00:16:43,750 --> 00:16:44,670
how are we supposed to

315
00:16:44,670 --> 00:16:45,960
proceed with the investigation?

316
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:47,760
Should we even continue with it?

317
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:50,480
We've been police officers for many years,

318
00:16:50,630 --> 00:16:52,440
working our tails off,
putting in overtime,

319
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,790
and sacrificing our health.

320
00:16:53,790 --> 00:16:55,440
We battle criminals on a daily basis

321
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:56,550
with our wits and courage.

322
00:16:56,550 --> 00:16:57,630
What's it all for?

323
00:16:58,930 --> 00:17:01,790
What lies before us now
is a complex social network.

324
00:17:01,870 --> 00:17:03,670
Hanzhou is just a small place.

325
00:17:03,690 --> 00:17:06,180
It's normal for people there
to be connected or related.

326
00:17:06,180 --> 00:17:07,440
But I can assure you

327
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:10,240
that we've handled every matter
by the book.

328
00:17:10,310 --> 00:17:11,030
For what?

329
00:17:11,109 --> 00:17:13,720
Just for fulfilling our duties, right?

330
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:15,589
Zhong, don't get so agitated.

331
00:17:15,589 --> 00:17:16,440
It sounds like

332
00:17:16,460 --> 00:17:17,609
you're refuting me.

333
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:20,880
I just want the best for the case.

334
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:22,109
If you truly care about these officers,

335
00:17:22,109 --> 00:17:23,829
you should be supportive of their work

336
00:17:23,829 --> 00:17:24,240
and...

337
00:17:24,240 --> 00:17:25,240
Alright. Enough.

338
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:32,350
It's my belief

339
00:17:34,070 --> 00:17:35,480
that the investigation

340
00:17:36,070 --> 00:17:36,870
must not stop.

341
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:38,680
Zhong,

342
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:42,000
aren't there many other officers
in your unit?

343
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:43,880
Make sure you reassure

344
00:17:43,880 --> 00:17:44,830
everyone.

345
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:46,310
Yes.

346
00:17:48,110 --> 00:17:49,960
Be flexible with the approach.

347
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:50,790
But

348
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:53,370
don't be swayed by public opinion.

349
00:17:53,550 --> 00:17:56,110
We need to neutralize
the negative social impact

350
00:17:56,110 --> 00:17:56,920
and strive for

351
00:17:57,110 --> 00:17:58,270
people's trust.

352
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:00,940
Most importantly,

353
00:18:02,310 --> 00:18:03,640
we must get things done.

354
00:18:05,750 --> 00:18:06,310
Yan,

355
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:08,360
what's your opinion?

356
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:10,960
Well...

357
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:12,990
I'll say a few words then?

358
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:16,160
So far,

359
00:18:16,790 --> 00:18:17,720
the matter

360
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:19,040
has escalated

361
00:18:20,550 --> 00:18:23,280
and caused
an extremely negative social impact.

362
00:18:23,550 --> 00:18:24,480
The credibility

363
00:18:24,510 --> 00:18:26,750
of the Municipal Bureau
and even the entire police force

364
00:18:26,750 --> 00:18:28,010
are being questioned.

365
00:18:28,310 --> 00:18:30,910
There isn't a single positive comment
online!

366
00:18:32,430 --> 00:18:34,760
However the investigation will turn out,

367
00:18:35,120 --> 00:18:37,380
we must quickly quell the public outcry.

368
00:18:37,450 --> 00:18:38,000
[Hanzhou Public Security]

369
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:38,550
First,

370
00:18:38,970 --> 00:18:39,900
get in contact

371
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:43,110
with whoever posted
the whistleblower materials

372
00:18:43,110 --> 00:18:44,920
to verify if the content is true

373
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:46,730
and if there's any defamation.

374
00:18:47,370 --> 00:18:48,070
Second,

375
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:51,920
disclose investigation progress
to the public soon,

376
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:53,590
so as to demonstrate our credibility

377
00:18:53,590 --> 00:18:54,400
and also...

378
00:18:54,830 --> 00:18:56,110
our sincerity.

379
00:18:58,400 --> 00:18:59,070
Third,

380
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,270
respond

381
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:04,510
with decisive action.

382
00:19:05,550 --> 00:19:06,680
The Municipal Bureau will fully cooperate

383
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:08,480
with all anti-smuggling operations.

384
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:09,950
We'll launch a formal investigation

385
00:19:09,950 --> 00:19:11,210
on Longwan Logistics.

386
00:19:11,750 --> 00:19:12,280
Besides,

387
00:19:13,310 --> 00:19:15,170
as for what was mentioned about Qin Feng

388
00:19:15,170 --> 00:19:16,170
and Wen Bo,

389
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:17,750
I suggest

390
00:19:18,100 --> 00:19:19,140
they be

391
00:19:19,640 --> 00:19:20,350
suspended.

392
00:19:20,370 --> 00:19:21,590
Consider it a vacation for them.

393
00:19:21,590 --> 00:19:23,050
When the results come out,

394
00:19:23,270 --> 00:19:24,600
we'll discuss further.

395
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:27,450
Director Ye, what do you think?

396
00:19:27,450 --> 00:19:28,270
[Hanzhou Public Security]

397
00:19:28,270 --> 00:19:28,880
I agree.

398
00:19:31,350 --> 00:19:32,480
Meeting adjourned.

399
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:54,350
-Captain Zhong.
-Captain Zhong.

400
00:19:54,350 --> 00:19:55,750
What will happen to them?

401
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,060
Captain Zhong,

402
00:20:00,240 --> 00:20:01,240
it's impossible.

403
00:20:01,290 --> 00:20:03,290
The two of them are by no means
involved in any shady stuff.

404
00:20:03,290 --> 00:20:04,810
We can all vouch for them.

405
00:20:06,310 --> 00:20:07,110
That's right.

406
00:20:08,460 --> 00:20:10,250
Wen Bo is such a good kid.

407
00:20:11,030 --> 00:20:13,400
How could he have possibly taken bribes?

408
00:20:13,790 --> 00:20:16,190
Someone's clearly trying to sabotage him!

409
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:18,800
Rest assured.

410
00:20:19,310 --> 00:20:20,310
I'll fight anyone

411
00:20:20,510 --> 00:20:21,730
who's after him to the end.

412
00:20:21,730 --> 00:20:23,460
I'm determined to protect him!

413
00:20:23,750 --> 00:20:24,610
That's my word.

414
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:27,070
Also,

415
00:20:28,030 --> 00:20:30,480
aren't there people
trying to obstruct our investigation?

416
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:32,430
Let's put as much effort as we can
into probing

417
00:20:32,430 --> 00:20:33,630
till the truth is out!

418
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:35,920
If you need help, come to me anytime.

419
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:39,030
How dare anyone touches my people?

420
00:20:39,030 --> 00:20:40,630
I'll show them what happens!

421
00:20:49,790 --> 00:20:50,480
Is he...

422
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:51,610
really your mentor?

423
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:53,960
Yes, I guess.

424
00:20:56,350 --> 00:20:57,270
Guys,

425
00:20:58,190 --> 00:20:59,850
Captain Zhong has stepped up.

426
00:20:59,940 --> 00:21:00,580
Look,

427
00:21:00,640 --> 00:21:02,480
Bo often treated us to boba tea,

428
00:21:02,480 --> 00:21:03,080
didn't he?

429
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:04,350
Captain Qin and Bo

430
00:21:04,350 --> 00:21:05,750
are just temporarily away.

431
00:21:05,750 --> 00:21:07,200
I believe justice will be restored

432
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:08,440
for them in time.

433
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:10,440
What should we do now?

434
00:21:11,030 --> 00:21:12,550
Now, we should do as much as we can

435
00:21:12,550 --> 00:21:15,220
to help them both weather through

436
00:21:15,310 --> 00:21:16,750
these difficult times.

437
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:18,580
Can we do it?

438
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:19,730
Absolutely!

439
00:21:20,030 --> 00:21:20,830
Let's get started!

440
00:21:20,830 --> 00:21:21,440
Yes!

441
00:21:23,550 --> 00:21:24,350
Impressive.

442
00:21:24,550 --> 00:21:26,610
You're starting to look like Mentor.

443
00:21:27,070 --> 00:21:29,070
It's time to show my true abilities.

444
00:21:30,460 --> 00:21:36,280
[Hanzhou Public Security Bureau]

445
00:21:40,240 --> 00:21:40,920
Nice and slow.

446
00:21:40,920 --> 00:21:41,790
I know.

447
00:21:41,920 --> 00:21:42,880
Alright.

448
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:45,590
Mentor,

449
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:47,290
please stay for dinner.

450
00:21:47,400 --> 00:21:48,110
Take a seat.

451
00:21:48,110 --> 00:21:49,060
I'll go cook.

452
00:21:49,480 --> 00:21:50,880
Just wait for 10 minutes.

453
00:21:51,240 --> 00:21:52,390
Where are those...

454
00:21:52,420 --> 00:21:54,160
pickles of yours? Serve some to Mentor.

455
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:55,550
Those are from ages ago.

456
00:21:55,550 --> 00:21:57,680
They must've gone bad
as I was hospitalized for a long time.

457
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:59,080
I should throw them away.

458
00:22:01,270 --> 00:22:02,560
I really mean it.

459
00:22:02,750 --> 00:22:03,610
I'm going home.

460
00:22:04,350 --> 00:22:07,010
My wife's waiting for me
to have dinner with her.

461
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:09,480
I cook really fast.

462
00:22:09,480 --> 00:22:10,510
Ten minutes is all I need.

463
00:22:10,510 --> 00:22:11,510
I'd rather leave.

464
00:22:15,140 --> 00:22:15,780
Hey.

465
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:18,500
What was that about?

466
00:22:19,110 --> 00:22:20,180
How old is he now?

467
00:22:20,210 --> 00:22:21,370
What do you want him to do?

468
00:22:21,370 --> 00:22:22,170
Tell me.

469
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:23,960
I didn't mean to have him do anything
for me

470
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:25,200
or chase him away.

471
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:26,870
I was just saying the pickles had gone bad

472
00:22:26,870 --> 00:22:28,170
and might get him sick,

473
00:22:28,190 --> 00:22:29,550
so we'd better serve him something better.

474
00:22:29,550 --> 00:22:31,330
Couldn't you have finished your sentence?

475
00:22:31,330 --> 00:22:33,400
But he left before I could finish it.

476
00:22:33,720 --> 00:22:35,850
Who would've known
he was so stubborn?

477
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:39,220
Let's drop that topic.

478
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:42,070
I've heard
Longwan Logistics is in trouble.

479
00:22:42,070 --> 00:22:43,070
Nothing serious.

480
00:22:43,110 --> 00:22:44,310
Don't worry about it.

481
00:22:45,350 --> 00:22:46,680
What will happen to you?

482
00:22:46,750 --> 00:22:48,240
What can possibly happen to me?

483
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:49,570
Who would dare touch me?

484
00:22:50,430 --> 00:22:51,480
Whoever comes after me

485
00:22:51,480 --> 00:22:53,230
means he or she has a guilty conscience.

486
00:22:53,230 --> 00:22:53,820
Right?

487
00:22:54,840 --> 00:22:57,370
Take care of your leg.
Don't think about that.

488
00:22:58,160 --> 00:22:59,510
What would you like to eat?

489
00:22:59,510 --> 00:23:00,930
Don't bother considering.

490
00:23:00,930 --> 00:23:03,050
I'll buy some pork trotters,

491
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:03,920
duck feet,

492
00:23:04,030 --> 00:23:05,770
and chicken feet from the market

493
00:23:05,770 --> 00:23:07,030
to make a soup that will help

494
00:23:07,030 --> 00:23:08,490
with your recovery. Okay?

495
00:23:08,750 --> 00:23:09,960
Fine. It's all up to you.

496
00:23:09,960 --> 00:23:10,590
Alright?

497
00:23:10,750 --> 00:23:12,440
It looks as if you're displeased.

498
00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:13,270
Just wait here.

499
00:23:13,270 --> 00:23:13,880
Okay.

500
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:28,270
Tianye,

501
00:23:29,480 --> 00:23:31,740
you've been too busy to talk to me lately.

502
00:23:32,070 --> 00:23:33,920
I'd hate to add to your burden.

503
00:23:35,060 --> 00:23:37,120
I want to do something to support you.

504
00:23:38,030 --> 00:23:39,750
We said we'd find time to talk,

505
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:42,080
but there has never been a right moment.

506
00:23:42,310 --> 00:23:44,570
You've been coming home later and later.

507
00:23:45,120 --> 00:23:48,120
My mind inevitably wanders
while I wait for you alone.

508
00:23:48,330 --> 00:23:50,160
I can't help but worry about you.

509
00:23:51,670 --> 00:23:53,300
At this rate,

510
00:23:53,320 --> 00:23:55,320
I'll only make things worse for you.

511
00:23:56,290 --> 00:23:58,490
I know you're hiding something from me.

512
00:23:58,920 --> 00:24:00,850
But you wouldn't tell me anything.

513
00:24:01,750 --> 00:24:02,750
In that case,

514
00:24:03,380 --> 00:24:05,180
we should spend some time apart.

515
00:24:06,400 --> 00:24:08,550
Let's wait till you settle
all issues at hand

516
00:24:08,550 --> 00:24:10,350
before we discuss our problems.

517
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:14,510
Jiangyan,

518
00:24:15,000 --> 00:24:16,370
have you seen Ziyi?

519
00:24:17,270 --> 00:24:19,270
She said she'd stay at her brother's place
for a few days.

520
00:24:19,270 --> 00:24:20,480
Did she not tell you?

521
00:24:25,060 --> 00:24:26,020
She did.

522
00:24:26,590 --> 00:24:27,720
She told me about it.

523
00:24:28,030 --> 00:24:28,790
Tianye,

524
00:24:29,130 --> 00:24:30,330
I want a word with you.

525
00:24:30,590 --> 00:24:32,120
Come meet me at the old dock.

526
00:24:35,400 --> 00:24:36,680
What can't you say to me at home?

527
00:24:36,680 --> 00:24:38,410
Why come all the way to the dock?

528
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:40,880
Look.

529
00:24:41,440 --> 00:24:44,040
Those deserted fishing boats are ours,
right?

530
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:48,790
Yes, the ones we used to fish with.

531
00:24:50,640 --> 00:24:51,240
See,

532
00:24:51,590 --> 00:24:53,120
these are paired with them.

533
00:24:54,750 --> 00:24:55,760
I never imagined

534
00:24:55,790 --> 00:24:59,050
that one day we the Longwan people
would discard our boats.

535
00:25:00,510 --> 00:25:02,170
There are bigger vessels now.

536
00:25:02,510 --> 00:25:03,310
It's normal...

537
00:25:03,310 --> 00:25:04,770
for these to be phased out.

538
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:06,160
Yeah.

539
00:25:06,400 --> 00:25:07,600
Everything changes.

540
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:10,000
Vessels change. People change.

541
00:25:10,550 --> 00:25:12,110
Changes take place all the time,

542
00:25:12,110 --> 00:25:12,830
right?

543
00:25:18,350 --> 00:25:19,590
Nobody else is around.

544
00:25:19,590 --> 00:25:21,320
Just speak your mind.

545
00:25:24,880 --> 00:25:26,010
I'm just wondering,

546
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:28,430
if nothing had happened to my family

547
00:25:28,430 --> 00:25:30,490
and that my parents were still alive,

548
00:25:30,500 --> 00:25:33,630
what my life would be like,
besides being free of hatred.

549
00:25:33,920 --> 00:25:35,680
What's done cannot be undone.

550
00:25:36,920 --> 00:25:37,680
Fate...

551
00:25:37,810 --> 00:25:39,120
is not to be changed.

552
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:40,550
But we can prevent

553
00:25:40,550 --> 00:25:42,080
bad things from happening.

554
00:25:44,350 --> 00:25:45,240
How?

555
00:25:54,510 --> 00:25:57,570
I heard someone took
the company's financial records,

556
00:25:57,640 --> 00:25:59,100
claiming it to be my order.

557
00:26:00,050 --> 00:26:01,200
Whoever did that

558
00:26:01,590 --> 00:26:03,320
must have his or her own reason.

559
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:05,450
For prevention, I suppose.

560
00:26:08,070 --> 00:26:09,110
I just hate for all of us

561
00:26:09,110 --> 00:26:10,510
to end up drifting apart.

562
00:26:13,440 --> 00:26:14,980
I must protect the family

563
00:26:15,070 --> 00:26:16,070
and Longwan...

564
00:26:18,400 --> 00:26:19,860
in my own way.

565
00:27:08,420 --> 00:27:08,980
[Public Security]

566
00:27:09,900 --> 00:27:10,530
[Customs]

567
00:27:11,590 --> 00:27:13,520
I've learned about all the matters

568
00:27:13,550 --> 00:27:14,310
you've mentioned.

569
00:27:14,310 --> 00:27:14,910
Madam Wen!

570
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:15,840
Madam Wen!

571
00:27:17,290 --> 00:27:18,040
Madam Wen!

572
00:27:18,070 --> 00:27:19,200
There are many cops outside.

573
00:27:19,200 --> 00:27:20,110
Go take a look!

574
00:27:20,110 --> 00:27:20,950
Cops?

575
00:27:21,240 --> 00:27:21,790
Hurry up!

576
00:27:21,790 --> 00:27:22,790
Maybe something's going on.

577
00:27:22,790 --> 00:27:23,510
Hurry.

578
00:27:27,180 --> 00:27:29,340
[Customs]

579
00:27:33,960 --> 00:27:36,770
[Police]

580
00:27:43,500 --> 00:27:44,890
Come on, open this box.

581
00:27:45,490 --> 00:27:47,350
