582
00:27:49,890 --> 00:27:50,470
[Financial Office]

583
00:28:36,270 --> 00:28:36,750
Come in.

584
00:28:37,530 --> 00:28:41,190
[May Wealth Flow In]

585
00:28:41,290 --> 00:28:41,410
[Search Warrent]

586
00:28:41,410 --> 00:28:42,060
Hello.

587
00:28:42,310 --> 00:28:43,480
We're anti-smuggling officers.

588
00:28:43,480 --> 00:28:44,890
Please cooperate with our inspection.

589
00:28:44,890 --> 00:28:50,300
[May Wealth Flow In]

590
00:28:51,640 --> 00:28:52,490
No problem.

591
00:28:55,630 --> 00:29:03,160
[Cold Storage]

592
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:09,370
