00:29:20,980 --> 00:29:22,560
[Watch your step]

596
00:29:27,420 --> 00:29:30,090
[Mind your hand]

597
00:29:59,160 --> 00:29:59,840
Tianfei.

598
00:30:00,320 --> 00:30:01,460
It's the last load, right?

599
00:30:01,460 --> 00:30:02,550
Any driving permit on you?

600
00:30:02,550 --> 00:30:03,030
Yes.

601
00:30:40,950 --> 00:30:45,310
[Qunhuan Trading Co., Ltd.]

602
00:31:00,470 --> 00:31:00,880
Dad.

603
00:31:02,020 --> 00:31:03,510
I'm off to Uncle Tianfei's.

604
00:31:03,510 --> 00:31:04,390
Wait. Where?

605
00:31:05,050 --> 00:31:06,050
Uncle Tianfei's.

606
00:31:06,510 --> 00:31:07,240
Why?

607
00:31:07,920 --> 00:31:09,640
He has the latest gaming console at home.

608
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:10,570
I want to play it.

609
00:31:10,590 --> 00:31:11,320
You can't go.

610
00:31:11,680 --> 00:31:12,240
Why not?

611
00:31:14,590 --> 00:31:17,310
Have you forgotten you got in trouble
in Longwan before?

612
00:31:17,310 --> 00:31:18,840
You're never in luck there.

613
00:31:19,390 --> 00:31:21,450
Is it because of the recent incident?

614
00:31:22,130 --> 00:31:23,260
What have you heard?

615
00:31:23,590 --> 00:31:24,590
It's all over the internet.

616
00:31:24,590 --> 00:31:26,590
Don't believe that nonsense online.

617
00:31:26,590 --> 00:31:27,920
People outside are just

618
00:31:28,070 --> 00:31:30,400
jealous of our financial success. Got it?

619
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:31,110
Dad,

620
00:31:31,850 --> 00:31:32,980
