621
00:31:33,350 --> 00:31:35,750
It's adult business. Don't be nosy, kiddo.

622
00:31:36,030 --> 00:31:36,750
Well,

623
00:31:36,750 --> 00:31:37,720
what's the name

624
00:31:37,740 --> 00:31:39,070
of that gaming console?

625
00:31:39,270 --> 00:31:40,130
I'll buy you one

626
00:31:40,430 --> 00:31:41,430
and play with you.

627
00:31:42,630 --> 00:31:44,090
Alright, dinner's ready.

628
00:31:44,290 --> 00:31:45,020
Let's go eat.

629
00:31:45,870 --> 00:31:47,930
All you ever want is to go out and play.

630
00:31:50,550 --> 00:31:51,000
Peng.

631
00:31:52,240 --> 00:31:53,110
Did anything...

632
00:31:53,110 --> 00:31:53,930
happen today?

633
00:31:53,950 --> 00:31:54,760
No.

634
00:31:54,790 --> 00:31:56,320
Just a routine inspection.

635
00:31:59,270 --> 00:32:00,610
How are things between you

636
00:32:00,610 --> 00:32:01,370
and Tianye?

637
00:32:02,480 --> 00:32:03,480
Is everything okay?

638
00:32:03,480 --> 00:32:04,260
Yes.

639
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:06,270
He's been busy lately, right?

640
00:32:06,270 --> 00:32:07,870
He can't sleep well at night.

641
00:32:07,960 --> 00:32:09,890
I can't either when the baby cries.

642
00:32:10,200 --> 00:32:11,790
So I decided to stay a few days here.

643
00:32:11,790 --> 00:32:12,270
Okay.

644
00:32:12,830 --> 00:32:14,350
-Stay for as long as you like.
-Zhao Peng!

645
00:32:14,350 --> 00:32:15,000
Zhao Peng!

646
00:32:15,220 --> 00:32:16,100
Where's Zhao Peng?

647
00:32:16,100 --> 00:32:16,730
Zhao Peng!

648
00:32:16,760 --> 00:32:17,850
Get back in.

649
00:32:21,030 --> 00:32:21,560
Uncle.

650
00:32:22,110 --> 00:32:23,350
-What's up?
-Zhao Peng.

651
00:32:23,350 --> 00:32:24,470
My grandson told me

652
00:32:24,510 --> 00:32:26,200
Longwan Logistics
is smuggling goods by water.

653
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:26,970
Is it true?

654
00:32:27,480 --> 00:32:29,000
Zhao Peng, is the information online

655
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:30,610
true or false?

656
00:32:30,830 --> 00:32:31,750
Yeah, Zhao Peng,

657
00:32:31,750 --> 00:32:33,160
do you know something?

658
00:32:33,190 --> 00:32:34,720
At least tell us what's really going on.

659
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:37,270
No, guys,
don't believe those rumors online.

660
00:32:37,310 --> 00:32:39,370
There was just a routine inspection.

661
00:32:39,750 --> 00:32:40,400
So all is fine?

662
00:32:40,400 --> 00:32:41,240
Yes, all is fine.

663
00:32:41,240 --> 00:32:42,720
When will the logistics company

664
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:44,390
resume operations?

665
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:45,790
Very soon.

666
00:32:45,920 --> 00:32:46,650
Zhao Peng,

667
00:32:46,830 --> 00:32:49,990
could it be the Longwan people
cooking up a scam?

668
00:32:50,150 --> 00:32:51,460
Don't be deceived.

669
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:53,830
Or you'll end up suffering, right?

670
00:32:53,830 --> 00:32:54,510
That's right.

671
00:32:54,510 --> 00:32:55,040
Exactly.

672
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:56,500
If you're worried,

673
00:32:56,590 --> 00:32:57,920
let me offer a solution.

674
00:32:58,070 --> 00:32:58,350
If necessary,

675
00:32:58,350 --> 00:33:00,700
we'll hold a villagers' meeting
to deliberate this matter

676
00:33:00,700 --> 00:33:02,850
and the possibility
to stop working with them.

677
00:33:02,850 --> 00:33:03,680
Now that all is fine,

678
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:05,000
there's no reason to quit. Right?

679
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:05,600
Right.

680
00:33:05,750 --> 00:33:07,160
We should continue working with Longwan.

681
00:33:07,160 --> 00:33:08,570
Tianye is good at making money.

682
00:33:08,570 --> 00:33:09,430
That's right.

683
00:33:09,480 --> 00:33:11,550
No, money shouldn't be our only focus.

684
00:33:11,550 --> 00:33:13,030
If they lack development potential,

685
00:33:13,030 --> 00:33:13,880
there's no point

686
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:14,880
in partnering with them,

687
00:33:14,880 --> 00:33:15,280
right?

688
00:33:16,010 --> 00:33:17,200
No, it's wrong.

689
00:33:17,590 --> 00:33:18,640
When there are profits,

690
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:20,130
why leave a business partner?

691
00:33:20,130 --> 00:33:21,480
Won't we be fools if we shrink

692
00:33:21,480 --> 00:33:23,000
from the opportunity to make money?

693
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:23,530
Exactly.

694
00:33:23,830 --> 00:33:25,560
You disagree with all my ideas.

695
00:33:26,090 --> 00:33:27,890
Maybe I'm just not up for the job.

696
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:29,500
Then why not replace me

697
00:33:29,620 --> 00:33:30,480
with someone else?

698
00:33:30,480 --> 00:33:31,810
-No way.
-That won't do.

699
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:32,510
Zhao Peng,

700
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:33,920
this job must be yours.

701
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:35,070
Who else could take it if not you?

702
00:33:35,070 --> 00:33:35,890
You must do it!

703
00:33:36,110 --> 00:33:36,480
Yeah.

704
00:33:36,830 --> 00:33:37,400
Zhao Peng,

705
00:33:37,400 --> 00:33:39,580
Liu Tianye only trusts you.

706
00:33:39,650 --> 00:33:40,740
How would we manage

707
00:33:40,760 --> 00:33:41,960
without you?

708
00:33:42,070 --> 00:33:43,180
Exactly!

709
00:33:43,350 --> 00:33:44,720
You're entrusted
with Zhao Village's interests.

710
00:33:44,720 --> 00:33:45,650
You can't just quit

711
00:33:45,650 --> 00:33:47,010
after receiving some benefits.

712
00:33:47,010 --> 00:33:48,470
Want to quit as you please?

713
00:33:48,500 --> 00:33:49,830
That's not how it works.

714
00:33:50,030 --> 00:33:50,440
Right, guys?

715
00:33:50,440 --> 00:33:51,360
-Right!
-Exactly!

716
00:33:51,360 --> 00:33:52,420
Zhao Peng,

717
00:33:52,590 --> 00:33:53,640
a person should

718
00:33:53,640 --> 00:33:55,530
follow through his commitments.

719
00:33:55,860 --> 00:33:56,850
Understood?

720
00:33:58,520 --> 00:33:59,010
Yes.

721
00:34:00,860 --> 00:34:01,430
I get it.

722
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:07,070
Based on the maximum dividend ratio
set by your company,

723
00:34:07,070 --> 00:34:08,960
[Longwan Logistics]

724
00:34:08,960 --> 00:34:11,510
there couldn't be this much money
in the account.

725
00:34:11,510 --> 00:34:12,330
Is it too much?

726
00:34:13,070 --> 00:34:14,929
How come it seems too little to me?

727
00:34:15,540 --> 00:34:16,739
What makes you say so?

728
00:34:18,920 --> 00:34:21,630
We the Longwan people
value family ties above all.

729
00:34:21,630 --> 00:34:23,219
Wenbo's father was my older brother.

730
00:34:23,219 --> 00:34:23,630
[Longwan Logistics]

731
00:34:23,630 --> 00:34:24,830
He died because of us.

732
00:34:25,670 --> 00:34:26,800
So, we decided to set part

733
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:27,920
of our earnings aside for Wen Bo

734
00:34:27,920 --> 00:34:28,800
and Mrs. Wen every time

735
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:30,460
dividends were distributed.

736
00:34:30,850 --> 00:34:32,449
They deserve this 5 million,

737
00:34:33,030 --> 00:34:34,110
or even 50 million,

738
00:34:34,469 --> 00:34:35,550
if you ask me.

739
00:34:38,600 --> 00:34:39,800
We owe them this much.

740
00:34:41,550 --> 00:34:44,080
Thank you for taking the time
with my inquiry.

741
00:34:44,949 --> 00:34:46,750
I should be the one thanking you.

742
00:34:48,280 --> 00:34:49,340
I'm counting on you

743
00:34:49,409 --> 00:34:50,540
for Wen Bo's matter.

744
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:51,460
No problem.

745
00:34:54,510 --> 00:34:55,179
Ms. Leng,

746
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:58,620
will Longwan Logistics' case

747
00:34:59,880 --> 00:35:01,100
affect Feng?

748
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:05,550
We'll conduct a thorough investigation

749
00:35:05,550 --> 00:35:06,810
and draw a conclusion.

750
00:35:07,480 --> 00:35:09,160
Personally speaking,

751
00:35:09,740 --> 00:35:10,870
I trust Captain Qin.

752
00:35:11,070 --> 00:35:11,930
So don't worry.

753
00:35:12,910 --> 00:35:13,910
Good to hear that.

754
00:35:16,000 --> 00:35:17,440
Has Feng mentioned

755
00:35:17,470 --> 00:35:18,530
Xu Li's case to you?

756
00:35:20,150 --> 00:35:21,310
Xu Li...

757
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:24,200
I know about her case.

758
00:35:25,110 --> 00:35:26,510
It was the exact reason
for Feng's transfer

759
00:35:26,510 --> 00:35:27,970
to Gutang Police Station.

760
00:35:31,250 --> 00:35:32,310
Xu Li and I

761
00:35:32,540 --> 00:35:34,600
grew up together as friends.

762
00:35:35,520 --> 00:35:37,780
I went with her to file the police report.

763
00:35:38,070 --> 00:35:38,840
Come to think of it,

764
00:35:38,840 --> 00:35:39,970
Feng and I have known

765
00:35:40,190 --> 00:35:41,990
each other for quite a long time.

766
00:35:43,070 --> 00:35:44,930
He and his fellows,

767
00:35:45,480 --> 00:35:46,000
in my opinion,

768
00:35:46,000 --> 00:35:47,760
are excellent police officers—

769
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:49,620
more dedicated than most others.

770
00:35:50,510 --> 00:35:52,200
But I guess Longwan Logistics' matter

771
00:35:52,200 --> 00:35:54,360
has caused much distress to Feng.

772
00:35:55,110 --> 00:35:56,970
Given that, I'd say he's somewhat

773
00:35:57,040 --> 00:35:57,820
affected.

774
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:02,030
If something comes up,

775
00:36:02,340 --> 00:36:03,670
I'll contact you again.

776
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:04,890
No need to see me out.

777
00:36:05,190 --> 00:36:05,630
Okay.

778
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:07,130
Take care, Ms. Leng.

779
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:15,810
How's Baoying doing at your place
during these days?

780
00:36:15,820 --> 00:36:16,820
He's doing great.

781
00:36:17,230 --> 00:36:18,160
Ziyi's with him.

782
00:36:18,300 --> 00:36:19,030
Don't worry.

783
00:36:23,350 --> 00:36:26,200
What are Ziyi and Tianye planning to do?

784
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:28,510
I don't know either.

785
00:36:29,510 --> 00:36:30,680
My sister

786
00:36:30,700 --> 00:36:32,500
has always been strong-minded.

787
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:35,600
She doesn't share everything
with her family.

788
00:36:35,670 --> 00:36:36,490
I...

789
00:36:37,070 --> 00:36:38,800
will ask her when I get a chance.

790
00:36:39,590 --> 00:36:42,000
If Ziyi is determined to get a divorce,

791
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:44,470
I won't object to it,
though I'm her mother-in-law.

792
00:36:44,470 --> 00:36:46,150
I'll respect her decision.

793
00:36:47,570 --> 00:36:49,150
You actually know better than anyone

794
00:36:49,150 --> 00:36:50,670
about everything that has happened

795
00:36:50,670 --> 00:36:52,070
between Ziyi and Tianye.

796
00:36:54,440 --> 00:36:55,610
We used to

797
00:36:55,750 --> 00:36:58,320
hold loads of grudges against each other.

798
00:36:59,250 --> 00:37:00,980
It was the fight against Ma Jin

799
00:37:01,000 --> 00:37:03,430
that brought our two villages together.

800
00:37:04,870 --> 00:37:06,160
During those difficult times,

801
00:37:06,160 --> 00:37:08,160
you chose to collaborate with us

802
00:37:08,250 --> 00:37:10,120
and offered much help to us.

803
00:37:10,560 --> 00:37:12,420
I've always kept all that in mind.

804
00:37:15,590 --> 00:37:18,200
Those hard times are finally behind us.

805
00:37:18,230 --> 00:37:20,060
Everyone has money now.

806
00:37:21,440 --> 00:37:22,200
But...

807
00:37:23,070 --> 00:37:24,400
do they really think...

808
00:37:25,470 --> 00:37:27,600
that money was earned fair and square?

809
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:30,240
Zhao Peng,

810
00:37:30,940 --> 00:37:33,600
why did you partner with Longwan
in the first place?

811
00:37:33,600 --> 00:37:36,350
Wasn't it to improve the villagers' lives?

812
00:37:36,490 --> 00:37:38,620
But look at what you guys are doing now.

813
00:37:39,200 --> 00:37:41,460
Is it really for the villagers' benefit?

814
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:43,150
You're their leader.

815
00:37:43,690 --> 00:37:44,920
If you lose your way,

816
00:37:44,940 --> 00:37:47,940
the villagers will end up going astray
along with you.

817
00:37:53,160 --> 00:37:54,770
I must set things straight.

818
00:37:55,870 --> 00:37:58,310
A shareholders' meeting
will be held in a few days.

819
00:37:58,310 --> 00:38:00,040
I hope to have your support.

820
00:39:36,710 --> 00:39:37,460
Jiangyan.
